node.text: Just watched Zianna Oliphant’s full speech and I’m in tears. This breaks breaks my heart 💔😢#blacklivesmatter ✊🏿
Not just jewelry…well mainly jewelry but we also have belts 🐉 ⭐️ 🦋
So have you figured out your ring size yet? New rings coming soon
The dagger through the skull’s eyes is dropping in a few days along with some other🔥🔥🔥 pendants 💀🗡 So excited 🖤 Stay tuned!!

The butterfly said “They can’t stop talking about my transformation. I can only do it once in my lifetime. If only they knew, they can do it at any time and in countless ways.” 🐛🦋 SO ALLOW YOURSELF TO TRANSFORM AS MANY TIMES AS YOU NEED TO BE FULLY HAPPY AND FREE 🦋🦋🦋 #necklace #ring #jewelry #jewellery
Do you ever feel like you’re from another dimension? I know I’m from another dimension 👽🌀 I’m my own kind of being 🤪
Do you want more skull jewelry? 💀☠️ #rings
